Package: jbrowseR
Title: R Interface to JBrowse 2 Genome Browser Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("JBrowse", "Team", , "jbrowse@gmod.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides R functions to access genomic data from the same sources
    used by JBrowse 2 genome browser. Supports BigWig, VCF, GFF3, BAM, and BED
    formats through a unified interface. Enables reproducible analysis by using
    the same data adapters as JBrowse 2.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    rlang
Suggests:
    rtracklayer,
    VariantAnnotation,
    Rsamtools,
    GenomicRanges,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/GMOD/jbrowseR
BugReports: https://github.com/GMOD/jbrowseR/issues
